help_define('_HELP_ICOPYRECORDS',           "=Copy records=\n\nYou can copy an existing record in mask \"[[Edit records]]\" by selecting option \"Copy\" in [[Main menu]].\n\n====\nNB: You can only copy records if you have been authorised to do so. An [[Administrator | administrator]] can provide authorisation.\n====\n\nThis will generate a new record with the same structure and data as the original. Other fields will usually be modified as well and the record should then be saved under [[ieditrecords|Edit records]] following the procedure described above.\n\nImportant: The new record contains a new [[iids|ID]] and it exists completely independently of the original, cf. [[ilinks|Links]] and [[inewrecord|Entering new records]]");
