help_define('_HELP_IDELETERECORDS',         "=Delete records=\n\nNB: You can only delete records if you have been authorised to do so. A [[isupervisor|Supervisor]] can provide authorisation.\n\nYou can delete an existing record by selecting option \"Delete\" in [[imainmenu|Main menu]] of mask [[ieditrecords|Edit records]].\n\nThere will be a security check, and the response must be \"Yes\" in order for the record to be deleted. The record will then be deleted and cannot be retrieved.   \n\nOnly records with no existing [[ireferencesofrecords|references]] can be deleted.");
