help_define('_HELP_IEXPORT8',               "=Export=\n\nIf you have authorisation, you can select \"Export\"  to export records from the system or to import new records in mask [[ioverviewrecords|overview of records]]\nin the [[imainmenu|main menu]]. \n\nUnless otherwise indicated, only records selected in mask [[ioverviewrecords|overview of records]] can be exported. Click on the link to the right of the format you want or right click and select option  \"save target under...\" to begin the export process.");
