help_define('_HELP_IHELPONHELP0',           "=Help on Help=\n\nThe program has a context-sensitive help function. You reach the help clicking on the little question mark anywhere.");
help_define('_HELP_IHISTORY0',              "=History=\n\nThe History function (\"previous\" and \"next\" funcions) of the Browser in use only partially functions with this programme, because numerous data and pages are generated by forms and these are no longer valid when you leave the page. \n\nFor that reason you should avoid using this function and, in the first instance, use the navigation options offered by the programme instead, namely [[imainmenu|main menu]].");
