help_define('_HELP_ILOGINLOGOUT',           "=Logging in and out=\n\nYou have to register with your user name and password in order to use the programme.  If the user name is identified and the password is correct, you are given access to the data activated for you. These data are determined by the \n[[isupervisor|Supervisor]].\n\nYou cannot determine your user name yourself. It will also be set by the Supervisor to ensure that each user name is only issued once. Usually, the user name is your first name and/or surname or an abbreviation of it.\n\nYou can set your password yourself, see [[isettingspassword|Password]].\n\nWhen you have finished your work, don't forget to log out. Simply click on \n[[imainmenu|mainmenu]] to the right on the symbol \"Logout\".");
