help_define('_HELP_IMAINMENU',              "=Main menu=\n\nThe '''main menu''' is at the top of the page. The most important tables can be called up directly using the main menu. You can access the other tables through the \"Etc.\" buttons on the far right.\n\nAt the second level you will find the actions available for the selected table or the selected record.");
