help_define('_HELP_INEWRECORD',             "=Entering new records=\n\nNB: You can only enter new records if you have been authorised to do so.  Authorisation can be provided by [[isupervisor|Supervisor]].\n\nYou can enter a new record by selecting the option \"Neu\" in the [[imainmenu|main menu]] in mask [[ieditrecords|edit records]]\nor [[ioverviewrecords|overview of records]].\n\nThe new record can then be edited and saved following the procedure described under [[ieditrecords|edit records]]. Some fields may be set on standard values - if you want to avoid this, use option \"Empty\" in the menu instead of \"New\".\n\nCf. [[icopyrecords|copy records]]");
