help_define('_HELP_IVIEW0',                 "=View=\n\nIt is possible for records to be displayed directly.  Go to the [[imainmenu|main menu]], click on mask [[ieditrecords|edit records]] and select \"view\". A new window will open displaying the record. \n\nThe presentation  of the individual record will vary according to the application.");
help_define('_HELP_IWIKI2',                 "=Simple Text Formatting Overview=\n\n[[box(0)]]\n'''Text formatting''' \n<nowiki>''italics'', '''bold'''</nowiki> etc. \n\n'''Text structure''' \n<nowiki>=</nowiki>headline level 1=<br />==headline level 2== \n\n'''Paragraph formatting''' \n<nowiki>:</nowiki>indent paragraph 1 time\n<nowiki>::</nowiki>indent paragraph 2 times \nright-aligned paragraph<nowiki>::</nowiki>\n<nowiki>::</nowiki>centered paragraph<nowiki>::</nowiki> \nline&lt;br&gt;break \n\n\n'''Enumerations'''\n<nowiki>-</nowiki>point 1\n<nowiki>-</nowiki>point 2\n<nowiki>1</nowiki>. point 1\n<nowiki>2.</nowiki> point 2 \n\n'''Tables'''\n<nowiki>|table|without|borders</nowiki> \n<nowiki>|table|with|border|</nowiki> \n<nowiki>||span|cells|</nowiki> \n<nowiki>|right-aligned cell::|</nowiki>\n<nowiki>|::centered cell::|</nowiki> \n\n\n[[boxwrap()]]\n\n'''Images'''\n<nowiki>[[image.gif]]</nowiki>&nbsp;&nbsp;<nowiki>[[image.gif|text]]</nowiki> \n<nowiki>[[right_aligned_image.gif::]]</nowiki>\n<nowiki>[[::left_aligned_image.gif]]</nowiki> \n\n\n'''Links'''\n<nowiki>http://external.link.com</nowiki>\n<nowiki>email@domain.com</nowiki> \n<nowiki>[[http://external.link.com]]</nowiki>\n<nowiki>[[http://external.link.com|text]]</nowiki> \n<nowiki>[[internal link]]</nowiki>\n<nowiki>[[internal link|text]]</nowiki> \n<nowiki>[[link|image.gif]]</nowiki>\n<nowiki>[[link|image.gif|text]]</nowiki> \n\n'''Lines/Boxes'''\n<nowiki>----</nowiki> \n<nowiki>====</nowiki>\ntext in a box \n<nowiki>====</nowiki>\n\n\n'''HTML'''\n&lt;a...>...&lt;/a>, &lt;b>...&lt;/b> etc. \n\n'''Avoid formatting'''\n&lt;nowiki&gt;...&lt;/nowiki&gt; \n[[boxend()]]");
